headline: What Does Stryker’s Latest Earnings Growth Mean for Its 2025 Valuation?
summary: If you’ve ever wondered what to do with Stryker stock, you’re definitely not alone. This medical devices giant has long been a favorite for growth-minded investors, but its recent market moves might have you second-guessing. After a small dip last month, Stryker’s share price has started to gain some traction again, up 2.7% in just the last week. Year to date, it’s notched a 4.4% return, and over the past three years, investors have seen a remarkable 76.7% gain. While the pace has slowed in...
